caption.p: ( a) GCD profile of an LOB using NiO-based Ti 3C 2 catalysts @ 100 mA g −1. ( b) GCD of NiO-Ti 3C 2-2 at various current densities. ( c) GCD profile of an LOB using NiO-based Ti 3C 2 catalysts @ 500 mA g −1. ( d) Cycling behavior of NiO-based Ti 3C 2 catalysts. ( e) GCD plot of NiO-Ti 3C 2-2 at a fixed current rate of 500 mA g −1. ( f, g) CV and electrochemical impedance analysis (EIS) plots of NiO-based Ti 3C 2 catalysts. ( h) Graphical representation of charge–discharge mechanisms in an LOB [ 128]. Copyright 2020 The American Chemical Society.
